headline: Forget Tech: Buy These 5 Non-Tech High Flyers of Q1
summary: Here we discuss five non-tech stocks that have provided double-digit returns year to date, defying the negative trends of U.S. stock markets. These are TPR, WEC, CNP, CME and CEH.
